2 |year=2002 |publisher=\u041f\u0440\u043e\u0444. \u041c\u0430\u0440\u0438\u043d \u0414\u0440\u0438\u043d\u043e\u0432 |location=\u0421\u043e\u0444\u0438\u044f |edition=\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0432\u044a\u0440\u0442\u043e \u0438\u0437\u0434\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435 |language=Bulgarian |pages=195\u2013197 |chapter=\u0411\u0430\u043d\u0430\u0442\u0441\u043a\u0438 \u0433\u043e\u0432\u043e\u0440 |chapterurl=http://www.kroraina.com/knigi/jchorb/st/st_2_b_vun_2.htm |isbn=954-430-846-6 }}\n* {{cite book |author=Prof. Ivanciov Margareta |title=Istorijata i tradicijite na balgarskotu malcinstvu ud Rumanija |url=http://nasaglas.link.ro/Utile/Ucebnik.pdf |format=PDF |publisher=Balgarsku Dru\u017estvu ud Ban\u00e1t&nbsp;\u2013  Rumanija, Editura Mirton |year=2006 |location=Timi\u015foara |language=Bulgarian|url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090305051006/http://nasaglas.link.ro/Utile/Ucebnik.pdf |archivedate=2009-03-05 }}\n* {{cite book |chapterurl=http://www.uni-klu.ac.at/eeo/BanaterBulgarisch.pdf |chapter=Banater Bulgarisch |language=German |last=Duli\u010denko |first=Alexander D |authorlink=Aleksandr Dulichenko |title=Enzyklop\u00e4die des Europ\u00e4ischen Ostens |accessdate=2007-03-30 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070926190649/http://www.uni-klu.ac.at/eeo/BanaterBulgarisch.pdf |archivedate=2007-09-26 }}\n* {{cite journal |title=To the problem of the ethnographic investigations of the internet communities (bulgariansfrombanat_worldwide case study) |first=Detelin |last=Lu\u010dev |url=http://ecsocman.edu.ru/db/msg/184746.html#_ftn19 |journal=Sociologija i Internet |accessdate=2007-04-14 |date=2004\u20132005 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20070407152915/http://www.ecsocman.edu.ru/db/msg/184746.html| archivedate= 7 April 2007 | url-status= live}}\n* {{cite book |title=\u0411\u044a\u043b\u0433\u0430\u0440\u0438\u0442\u0435 \u043a\u0430\u0442\u043e\u043b\u0438\u0446\u0438 \u0432 \u0422\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0441\u0438\u043b\u